The paper focuses on a tool for code reviewer recommendation, which is a software engineering task (cs.SE). The tool also considers the developer's experience in certain specialized technologies, which could fall under the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY) or information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the tool is designed as a Google Chrome plug-in, which could relate to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) or social and information networks (cs.SI).
